snippet.title: JUMP FORCE - Awakening Trailer | X1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Change the tide of battle with Ultimate Transformations! Watch Goku SSGSS and Vegeta SSGSS go all out against Golden Frieza in JUMP FORCE!

Unite to fight when JUMP FORCE releases on Feb. 15, 2019. Pre-order today: https://bandainam.co/JumpForcePO
